{"tid":1604830,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[759中伏系列]大家咪買黑色包裝果隻炸豬皮！","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:14:46.000Z","uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1005d49f5d8139a521a84ce9c032364e5c7084b6","tid":1604830,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"早個星期見到，未食過咪試吓囉&hellip;初時食係覺得幾唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，脆脆地咸咸地送吓啤酒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲食上隱，再買多兩包食，點知就出事了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n噚晚又食食吓送啤酒，食到尾咬到粒嘢係苦嘅，初時唔為意仲咬多左吓，點知係勁苦，吐出嚟浪口浪幾次個口仲係苦苦地，我好懷疑唔係炸燶咁簡單，直情有可能係屎嚟，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲工人可能將唔乾淨嘅嘢倒埋落去炸都唔出奇，仆佢個街你食到粒嘢苦，你可以去告佢咩，我越諗越唔對路，連未食果包都掉尻埋了!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9295be4571259c767e374ccfcf0adf7330ccb56d","tid":1604830,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"豬定人屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a27573a9228ab8928cdfe872d560e301b9448f7","tid":1604830,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9295be4571259c767e374ccfcf0adf7330ccb56d","tid":1604830,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"豬定人屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"同自己講，豬耳屎嚟姐，洗乜驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><